    "Beside it, a massive cooling tower reminds us that computing is still an industrial enterprise that uses a lot of energy.",
    "While Blue Waters was under construction, as literacy researchers with an interest in digital media, we mused: just about every published word has already been ingested into the universal library of the internet.",
    "What then, if the relationship of every word to every other word could be calculated?",
    "At the time, this was even too big for Blue Waters.Well, now it has happened, more or less.",
    "It's called Generative AI."
